selectEntry

public void selectEntry(String label)
Selects an entry of this Dropdownbox by its label. If the label is null or marked as null, the operation is not executed. It the label is marked as empty, it will be replaced with "".

Specified by:
selectEntry in interface Dropdownbox
Parameters:
label - Label of the entry to select.

assertHasLabels

public void assertHasLabels(String... labels)
Checks if this Dropdownbox has the expected labels. The check fails if:
  • order of the Labels is wrong
  • not every Label is mentioned
  • a wrong Label is mentioned
If only one label is passed and it is null or marked as null, the operation will not be executed.

Specified by:
assertHasLabels in interface Dropdownbox
Parameters:
labels - which should be checked
